uiFields.expression: var symbolentity=$feature.category1+$feature.category2+$feature.category3;var echelon = $feature.echelon; if(isEmpty(echelon) || indexof(['30', '35', '15'], $feature.symbolset) != -1) { echelon = $feature.array; if(isEmpty(echelon) || indexof(['15'], $feature.symbolset) != -1) {echelon = $feature.mobility; if(isEmpty(echelon)) {echelon = '00';}}} var modifier1 = $feature.modifier1; if(isEmpty(modifier1)){modifier1 = '00'} var modifier2 = $feature.modifier2; if(isEmpty(modifier2)){modifier2 = '00'}  return '10' + $feature.context + $feature.identity + $feature.symbolset + $feature.status + $feature.indicator + echelon + symbolentity + modifier1 + modifier2;
